{"id": 415, "genre": 1001, "title": "你理想中的手机是怎样的？", "description": "理想是人生的太阳，我都快被自己晒死了。", "record_count": 6952, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20160702200957lMoRQrqV0P8SWJGT.jpg", "page_style": 0, "category": 2, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2015-07-13T13:32:12Z", "options": [{"id": 3720, "content": "五六年不过时\n是个“艺术品”", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 142198}, {"id": 3776, "content": "一按就变身", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 142491}, {"id": 4057, "content": "像 夺命手机  一样", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 144225}, {"id": 4063, "content": "最好是透明的，薄薄的，玩什么都不卡的，手机不发热的，造型多样的", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 143126}, {"id": 3558, "content": "上网不要钱", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 39258}, {"id": 3561, "content": "没有内置系统软件~ ~ ~ ", "image": null, "praise_count": 9, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 136181}, {"id": 3559, "content": "手机的涂层永远不会脱落 ", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 136181}, {"id": 3562, "content": "它自己识别软件内存问题 进行自动定期清理", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 136181}, {"id": 3564, "content": "能畅通无阻的视讯通话 即使没WiFi情况下", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 136181}, {"id": 3563, "content": "像Baymax一样暖心", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 136181}, {"id": 3906, "content": "iPhone6的正面+iPhone5的背面+Nokia1020的相机+太阳能充电", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 143295}, {"id": 3619, "content": "预装ios", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 119991}, {"id": 4097, "content": "个性化的", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 144567}, {"id": 4162, "content": "光动能，或者机械动能都好，总之，无时无刻，不用担心没电", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 90932}, {"id": 3608, "content": "性能完爆当今台式机", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1212373}, {"id": 3605, "content": "握在手上没有不适感，网速像素一流，所有程序全靠语音控制", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 141666}, {"id": 4254, "content": "有64T超大内存", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 129495}, {"id": 3811, "content": "悬浮控制，立体投射", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 93731}, {"id": 3494, "content": "不对，是以下所有", "image": null, "praise_count": 16, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 75648}, {"id": 3495, "content": "以上所有除了李易峰", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 136904}, {"id": 3500, "content": "能刷所有包，兼容一切", "image": null, "praise_count": 10, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 139628}, {"id": 3501, "content": "意念控制", "image": null, "praise_count": 101, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 122927}, {"id": 3503, "content": "有全息投影", "image": null, "praise_count": 98, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 126949}, {"id": 3497, "content": "我也要买", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 140953}, {"id": 3498, "content": "以上功能我想的手机都有", "image": null, "praise_count": 54, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 139695}, {"id": 3499, "content": "屏幕摔不碎", "image": null, "praise_count": 159, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 112264}, {"id": 3496, "content": "智能、个性和安全", "image": null, "praise_count": 45, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 132404}, {"id": 3533, "content": "现实点，按照二手市场99新价格以旧换新。对，说的是iPhone。", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 58260}, {"id": 3534, "content": "足够容量，足够电量，足够品质，足够性能，足够美观。", "image": null, "praise_count": 10, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 136410}, {"id": 3536, "content": "不再需要玻璃屏幕", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 140555}, {"id": 3538, "content": "长时间待机至少1个月以上，和个人绑定不用sim卡，安全和隐私保证不受威胁的前提下，app越多越好。", "image": null, "praise_count": 7, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 124359}, {"id": 3539, "content": "柔性屏幕，手势感应，5m内无线充电，24小时网络不断，可以当投影仪", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 38139}, {"id": 3540, "content": "成为我的私人助理，没它我就是个傻子", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 138575}, {"id": 3541, "content": "能当女朋友用", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 141236}, {"id": 3544, "content": "快 功能简洁 能上网 接打电话 照相  ", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 137201}, {"id": 3537, "content": "不用贴膜带保护套 怎么摔摔不坏怎么划划不坏 还不卡就行。", "image": null, "praise_count": 10, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 69901}, {"id": 4317, "content": "不卡", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 137789}, {"id": 4353, "content": "据说哪里骂EXO傻逼都会有人赞？", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 146023}, {"id": 4360, "content": "随时随地都有点，轻薄，无边框，屏占比高，", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 101526}, {"id": 3681, "content": "不要钱", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 142083}, {"id": 3481, "content": "哈哈", "image": "img/option/option/201606042349110JeswhimF6P3nVOc.jpg", "praise_count": 10, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1}, {"id": 3484, "content": "帅", "image": null, "praise_count": 9, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 120091}, {"id": 3486, "content": "无论怎么玩都不发烧", "image": null, "praise_count": 383, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 107047}, {"id": 3488, "content": "李易峰", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 140933}, {"id": 3483, "content": "成为虚拟的，随时可以转换成各种物品操作，墨镜，镜子，玻璃，各种清晰的物体，用脑电波认证", "image": null, "praise_count": 28, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 140918}, {"id": 3485, "content": "广角的，高清的", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 132194}, {"id": 3487, "content": "真•飞行模式", "image": null, "praise_count": 67, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 140316}, {"id": 3504, "content": "好看，不用充电，再便宜点。", "image": null, "praise_count": 38, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 140980}, {"id": 3505, "content": "可以变成女朋友", "image": null, "praise_count": 20, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 140987}, {"id": 3506, "content": "像一个手机.", "image": null, "praise_count": 9, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 94460}]}